---
---

<section class="author" id="author">
  <div class="author-inner">
    <div class="author-grid">
      <div class="author-photo-wrapper">
        <img src="/author-photo.jpeg" alt="Rasmus Bornhoft Schlunsen" class="author-photo" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="author-content">
        <h2>About the author</h2>
        <h3>Rasmus Bornhoft Schlunsen</h3>
        <p>
          With over 15 years in the software industry, Rasmus has built everything from Django
          database backends and embedded systems to Rust CLI tools and open-source libraries
          used by thousands. He's an active open-source contributor with projects like
          <a href="https://github.com/schlunsen/django-timescaledb" target="_blank">django-timescaledb</a>
          and <a href="https://github.com/schlunsen/rana" target="_blank">rana</a>.
          Currently, he works as an AI R&D Engineer at <a href="https://clovrlabs.com" target="_blank">Clovrlabs.com</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          He knows what a production incident feels like at 2am and what it takes to ship real
          products. Now he's navigating the shift to agentic engineering — and writing the
          playbook he wished he had.
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rasmusbs/" target="_blank" class="linkedin-link">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" style="vertical-align: -2px; margin-right: 4px;">
              <path d="M5 12l5-5 5 5" />
              <path d="M10 7v10" />
              <rect x="2" y="2" width="16" height="16" rx="3" />
            </svg>
            Connect on LinkedIn &rarr;
          </a>
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .author {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    position: relative;
  }

  .author::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-border), transparent);
  }

  .author-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .author-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .author-photo-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border: 3px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .author-photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }

  .author-photo-wrapper:hover .author-photo {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .linkedin-link {
    color: var(--color-accent-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .linkedin-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }


  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .author-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .author-illustration {
      aspect-ratio: 16/9;
      max-height: 250px;
    }
  }
</style>
